											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[ChristianD] PLYR takes the marble out from inventory and stretches their arm above the center of the ritual circle. PLYR closes their fist around the marbel and hold for a while. The PLYR then drops the marble to the floor. PLYR startled back, reacting to the floor ripples." />
										</node>
